{"tid":505690,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解吳雨霏首座右銘可以咁癲","createTime":"2017-12-21T11:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T15:03:06.000Z","uid":53947,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9b75b43363e7e4b777431e7b083f50214cc454d4","tid":505690,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"有更心跳選擇而比我遠遠優勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如何專一都想轉性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全講出毒撚嘅心聲<br />\n點解可以咁入肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d60177aed8f94573f6be2f5fd4e082b1c7e5626","tid":505690,"uid":12696,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"吳雨霏 <br />\n<br />\n座右銘<br />\n<br />\n作詞：方傑<br />\n作曲：walter wong<br />\n編曲：johnny yim<br />\n監製：gary chan<br />\n<br />\n很信命當我每次哭<br />\n亦只有結他聲<br />\n喃喃自語數星星<br />\n孤單也像注定<br />\n祈求被愛的溫馨<br />\n呼天都不應已經很適應<br />\n我心事誰又會在意想聽<br />\n<br />\n很冷靜知道我愛的<br />\n定把我當佈景<br />\n平凡像我這一種<br />\n今天要認了命<br />\n才能學會不貪心<br />\n碰不到戀愛也毫無反應<br />\n單戀相戀失戀說穿了儘是陷阱<br />\n放手得我有這本領<br />\n<br />\n一個自愛也好<br />\n越對我好越需要控制我反應<br />\n對未來沒信心怎張開眼睛<br />\n<br />\n花花世界太過美哪有我蹤影<br />\n怕有天放心後才給我最愛拋棄<br />\n我要謹守我座右銘<br />\n<br />\n很信命不信有美好<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞  <br />\n幸福過更冷清<br />\n同情沒法把不安<br />\n驅走以示確定<br />\n原來避免輸不起<br />\n退出的方法叫遺忘本性<br />\n不甘不忍不想我只有越坐越靜<br />\n我的快樂就像泡影<br />\n<br />\n一個自愛也好<br />\n越對我好越需要控制我反應<br />\n對未來沒信心怎張開眼睛<br />\n<br />\n花花世界太過美哪有我蹤影<br />\n怕有天放心後才給我最愛拋棄<br />\n我要謹守我座右銘<br />\n<br />\n派對滿佈愛情來臨的風景<br />\n獨自妒忌別人誰能夠高興<br />\n注定無人來示愛我都不作聲<br />\n<br />\n即使一個自愛也好<br />\n越對我好越需要控制我反應<br />\n對未來還沒信心怎張開眼睛<br />\n<br />\n花花世界太過美哪有我蹤影<br />\n有更心跳選擇而比我遠遠優勝<br />\n如何專一都想轉性<br />\n與情人齊眉白髮問誰可保證"},{"pid":"aa87b928cb51c9fa3e8a5118c035f5283ad27412","tid":505690,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:54:50.000Z","msg":"花花世界太過美"},{"pid":"e869a9430d8938caa9ca5bbcb808854c7135d4e0","tid":505690,"uid":2643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"很信命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a9682d6a27b9de7de418f928439b2283490fe3","tid":505690,"uid":10269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"花花世界太過美哪有我蹤影<br />\n有更心跳選擇而比我遠遠優勝<br />\n如何專一都想轉性<br />\n與情人齊眉白髮問誰可保<br />\n<br />\n呢段世界級 我聽完喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad79d6ebf5e8d8df79e86bf54cb118b2a4b002d4","tid":505690,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"夠鳩氣！"},{"pid":"0c845766416a43d5d68dcce950897f8bebaf2ebf","tid":505690,"uid":33610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"花花世界太過美哪有我蹤影"},{"pid":"c65b34d2af48378ec57f9311463f39754b630f15","tid":505690,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"咁多年前嘅歌<br />\n我電話入面仲有"},{"pid":"6308e6ccc22264aa944323f270ac2a0453ce1dd0","tid":505690,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97267bc27ba23e03ceffb9592ca6d32b25ddbb7","tid":505690,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aa51aa617539ace0e3a9b1666bc138c85b3d22e","tid":505690,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:03:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82a7419b731f8bcfd95a71521f8b8753fd26a23d","tid":505690,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:04